%e A004135 a(4)=6: the set {0,1,2,4} is such a subset of Z_6, since 0+1, 0+2, 0+4, 1+2, 1+4 and 2+4 are all distinct in Z_6; also, no such 4-element set exists in any smaller cyclic group.
